parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "Spack",
  "details": {
    "software": [
      "Bash",
      "Python",
      "Git",
      "Spack",
      "GCC",
      "Julia",
      "Matplotlib",
      "Pandas",
      "Scipy",
      "JupyterLab",
      "IJulia"
    ],
    "resource_requirements": {
      "nodes": 1,
      "time": "04:00:00",
      "modules": [
        "python",
        "gcc",
        "julia"
      ]
    },
    "environment_variables": [
      "MYDIR",
      "TMPDIR",
      "SPACK_USER_CONFIG_PATH"
    ],
    "commands": [
      "module purge",
      "module load python",
      "git --version",
      "ml conda",
      "mkdir -p myspack/level00",
      "cd myspack/level00",
      "rm -rf spack",
      "git clone -c feature.manyFiles=true https://github.com/spack/spack.git",
      "module unload conda",
      "source `pwd`/spack/share/spack/setup-env.sh",
      "ml gcc",
      "spack compiler find",
      "sed -i$backup \"s,root: \$spack,root: $MYDIR/install,\" spack/etc/spack/defaults/config.yaml",
      "sed -i$backup \"s,\$spack/share/spack,$MYDIR/modules,\" spack/etc/spack/defaults/modules.yaml",
      "sed -ib \"s/- tcl/- lmod/\" spack/etc/spack/defaults/modules.yaml",
      "spack repo create myrepo",
      "spack repo add myrepo",
      "mkdir -p myrepo/packages/julia",
      "cp $STARTDIR/julia.py myrepo/packages/julia/package.py",
      "spack install julia",
      "module unload gcc",
      "module load julia",
      "which julia",
      "module load gcc",
      "spack install python@3.10.2 +tkinter",
      "module load python",
      "which python",
      "python -m pip install update",
      "which pip3",
      "pip3 install matplotlib",
      "pip3 install pandas",
      "pip3 install scipy",
      "pip3 install jupyterlab",
      "julia ij",
      "jupyter-lab --no-browser"
    ]
  }
}
```
